                        <title xml:lang="en">Commentary on the book of Jeremiah </title>
                        
                        
                        
                        <note>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>A fragment of the commentary on Jeremiah 2:17-31, 3:17-5:9, 5:14-9:2, 9:25-10:25, 11:6-20, 23:2-4, 7-10, 17-19, 22-25, 31:6-7, 21-22, 31:33-32:9, 32:12-15, 22-44, 33:9-26, 34:2-36:31, 37:1-38:5.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>The biblical text is written in large Arabic characters (using a phonetic transcription), provided with the Hebrew vowel-points and accents in red ink. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>An Arabic translation accompanies each verse. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Some masoretic notes. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </note>
                     
                     
                     
